# Test API Endpoints Locally
# Use with VS Code REST Client extension or similar

### Test Job Search (Step 1)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/jobs/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Software Engineer",
  "location": "Amsterdam"
}

### Test Find Emails (Step 2)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/jobs/find-emails
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jobs": [
    {
      "job_id": "test-1",
      "employer_name": "Google",
      "employer_website": "https://www.google.com",
      "job_title": "Software Engineer"
    }
  ]
}

### Test Generate Cover Letter (Step 3)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/jobs/generate-cover
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jobs": [
    {
      "job_id": "test-1",
      "employer_name": "Google",
      "job_title": "Software Engineer",
      "job_description": "We are looking for a talented software engineer...",
      "hrEmail": "careers@google.com"
    }
  ],
  "resumeText": "Experienced software engineer with 5 years of experience in React, Node.js, and Python. Built scalable web applications serving millions of users.",
  "userName": "John Doe"
}
